Package org.hms.services.appointment

Class AppointmentOutcome

java.lang.Object
org.hms.services.appointment.AppointmentOutcome
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class AppointmentOutcome extends Object implements Serializable
The AppointmentOutcome class represents the outcome of an appointment. It includes details such as appointment ID, patient ID, type of appointment, consultation notes, and prescribed medications.
